Author: zoonosis
Title: [BXUNTY] FiiiCoin OFFICIALY BOUNTY CAMPAIGN! | www.fiii.io |
Body: FiiiCoin Official Bounty Campaign Thread The Bounty Campaign will run from September 12th - November 13th!     To get in touch with the Bitcointalk BXUNTY Team, simply visit: www.t.me/BXUNTY    For the Bitcointalk Bounty Campaign, up to 5,000,000 FiiiCoin have been reserved to be distributed to participants. FiiiCoin (Fiii) are cryptocyrrency tokens which will be distributed among the participants in the bounty campaign based on stakes earned in each bounty component, given the allocations as seen below.  Bounty Components 1. FiiiCoin Registration Campaign - 5% 2. Telegram Campaign - 5% 3. Facebook Campaign- 20% 4. Twitter Campaign - 20% 5. Article/Media Campaign - 30% 6. Translation Campaign - 10% 7. Signature Campaign - 10%  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- The Master Spreadsheet can be found Here! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  In order to confirm bounty participation and receive your FIII, please fill out this FORM!   1. FiiiCoin Website Campaign - 5%  Official FiiiCoin Website  Rewards: • 1 stake for registering on www.Fiii.io - THIS IS MANDATORY TO EARN TOKENS!  Guidelines: • Submit your email address on www.Fiii.io • Enter the same email address in the registration form.  How to Apply: FiiiCoin Website Registration Form  Check FiiiCoin Campaign Spreadsheet: Here   2. FiiiCoin Telegram Campaign - 5%  Rewards: • Telegram Channel Registration: 1 Stake  Guidelines: • To earn 1 Share, you need to Join our official Telegram channel. • You must remain in the Telegram channel until conclusion of the bounty campaign! • YOU MUST DIRECT MESSAGE THE FOLLOWING CODE TO @CRYPTOBOUNTYMANAGER ON TELEGRAM. DO NOT POST YOUR CONFIRMATION OF PARTICIPATION IN THE FIIICOIN CHANNEL OR YOU MAY BE DISQUALIFIED!  *SEND THIS IN A DIRECT MESSAGE TO @CRYPTOBOUNTYMANAGER ON TELEGRAM. DO NOT POST IN THE CHANNEL OR IN THIS THREAD!* Code: #JOINFIIICOINTELEGRAM  Bitcointalk Username: Telegram Username: @   How To Apply: Join our Telegram Group Telegram Registration Form  Check Telegram Spreadsheet: Here   3. FiiiCoin Facebook Campaign - 20%  Official FiiiCoin Facebook  Rewards: • 2 stakes / 1 Facebook Post about FiiiCoin • 1 stakes / 1 Facebook Share of FiiiCoin account post  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, FILL IN YOUR WEEKLY REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've reached 5 Posts & 5 stakes. Weekly Facebook Report Form  Guidelines: • Follow and like the official FiiiCoin Facebook page until after the end of the token sale • One facebook account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. • Your facebook account must have at least 500 friends. • All posts AND profiles will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. • MAXIMUM 5 POSTS WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 5 FACEBOOK shares WEEKLY • Maximum 15 stakes Earned WEEKLY • Posts and Profile must be public. • Submit weekly forms by latest the day the week is over in order to earn your stakes.  How to Apply: Facebook Registration Form  Check Facebook Spreadsheet: Here   4. FiiiCoin Twitter Campaign - 20%  Official FiiiCoin Twitter  Rewards: • 2 stakes / 1 Tweet about FiiiCoin • 1 stakes / 1 Retweet of FiiiCoin account tweet  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, FILL IN YOUR WEEKLY REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've reached 5 Tweets & 5 Retweets. Weekly Twitter Report Form  Guidelines: • You must follow @FiiiLab until after the end of the token sale. • One twitter account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. • Your twitter account must have at least 300 authentic followers. • All tweets will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. • Twitter Audit must be better than 80% (No Bot Behavior) • MAXIMUM 5 Retweets WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 5 Tweets WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 15 stakes WEEKLY • Submit weekly forms by latest the day the week is over in order to earn your stakes. • A Tweet must include at least one hashtag: #FiiiCoin #FIII  How to Apply: Twitter Registration Form  Check Twitter Spreadsheet: Here   5. FiiiCoin Articles/Media Campaign - 30%  Rewards: • All submitted Articles will receive 1 stake. • All submitted Videos will receive 2 stakes.  Guidelines: • A maximum of three articles and/or videos are eligible for stakes. • All articles or blog posts must be publicly viewable. • The platform through which you publish must be relevant and there must be an audience. • Videos must be 3 minutes long and include the links to our website (www.Fiii.io) in the description as well as the participants' Bitcointalk username. • Pieces should be at least 400 words and include the links to our website (www.Fiii.io)  How to Apply: FiiiCoin Article/Media Registration Form  Check Article/Media Campaign Spreadsheet: Here   6. FiiiCoin Translation Campaign - 10%  Rewards: • Whitepaper Translation: 250 stakes • Whitepaper Updates: 25 stakes Each Update • ANN Thread Translation: 75 stakes • ANN Thread Updates: 2 stakes Each Post  Guidelines: • TRANSLATORS WHO APPLY FOR ‘ALL’ WILL BE GIVEN PRIORITY • Absolutely no google translator is permitted to be used. Participants using google translator will not be accepted and if a google translation is submitted, that translator will be blacklisted! • Please do not submit a request to translate unless you are fluent in the translated language and in English. • Announcement Thread translators are expected to moderate the thread and regularly update the thread with news, info, posts, etc from the original FiiiCoin Ann Thread or social medias. Each translated update post will earn an additional 2 stakes! • If Announcement Thread translators do not make a reasonable attempt to regularly update the thread, a 75% reduction in share will be applied! Make minimum 1 update per week and this reduction will not apply! • Managers/Owners reserve the right to make minor, reasonable changes to the rules.  How to Apply: To reserve, please post:  • Your Language: • Reference to previous works (at least 3): • Translating Whitepaper, ANN thread, One-Pager or all:  Once you are messaged, you will fill out the Translation Registration Form, and show up on the spreadsheet below.  Completed Translations:  Chinese Whitepaper & Chinese Announcement Thread Croatian Whitepaper & Croatian Announcement Thread Filipino Whitepaper & Filipino Announcement Thread French Whitepaper & French Announcement Thread Hindi Whitepaper & Hindi Announcement Thread Polish Whitepaper & Polish Announcement Thread Romanian Whitepaper & Romanian Announcement Thread Russian Whitepaper & Russian Announcement Thread Spanish Whitepaper & Spanish Announcement Thread Turkish Whitepaper & Turkish Announcement Thread Ukrainian Whitepaper & Ukrainian Announcement Thread Vietnamese Whitepaper & Vietnamese Announcement Thread Korean Announcement Thread    Check Translation Campaign Spreadsheet: Here    7. FiiiCoin Signature Campaign - 10%  Rewards: 1. Newbie: 5 stakes/Week 2. Jr. Member: 15 stakes/Week 3. Member: 20 stakess/Week 4. Full Member: 30 stakes/Week 5. Sr. Member: 50 stakes/Week 6: Hero Member: 65 stakes/Week 7: Legendary Member: 80 stakes/Week  +5 stakes/Week for wearing our Avatar!  Guidelines: • Must make at least 5 constructive posts on Bitcoin Talk Forum per week. • No negative trust accounts please • The Bounty Manager will update spreadsheets every week and check that the signature is still being used week after week.
